data.description:
This Home displays home-ownership pride from beginning to end. It is in pristine condition and has a plethora of upgrades and extra features: Tile throughout the whole home, Accent walls, 5 Sonance 8 in Surround Sound Speakers in Living Area, Upgraded walk-in showers in both bathrooms, Granite Countertops, Backsplash, Double extended sized Rain Showerhead in primary bedroom, Dimmable Lights in entertainment area, Fans in all bedrooms, Security Door Lock, Ring Door Bell, Great 4'x12' storage in side of home and an INCREDIBLY AMAZING Backyard Landscaping including a Pergola, Fence, Lights, Turf and Concrete !!!

This home makes your dreams of having a personal Oasis in your backyard a reality... Come and make this home yours before someone else does.
